| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3470 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 70fddc74-6043-5832-b84d-a20ca5fbec5c"
